FBIS3-57716 "drsov019_g_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-019 Document Type:Daily Report 29 Jan 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Prime Minister, Officials View Shushkevich Ouster Officers Union Thanks Deputies for Ouster WS2801085394 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 0400 GMT 28 Jan 94 WS2801085394 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Language: Belarusian Article Type:BFN [Text] The Council of the Officers' Union of Belarus has issued a statement thanking the people's deputies for expressing their nonconfidence in Shushkevich as one of the gravediggers of the USSR. This step is recognized by the Officers' Union as a beginning of the path toward condemning the Viskuli [location where Yeltsin, Kravchuk, and Shushkevich signed agreement to create CIS] plot.
